description: Demolition of existing building and erection of a part 5- to 13-storey building with communal terraces, comprising a total of 115 flats (54 x one-bedroom, 46 x two-bedroom and 15 x three-bedroom) on upper floors, ground-floor commercial unit (Use Classes A1, A2, A3), basement parking and associated landscaping and amenity space and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 3rd February 2011 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended
